{"tha-ap122:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap122:0.2":"Mahaparivaravagga ","tha-ap122:0.3":"Jatipujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap122:1.1":"“Jayantassa vipassissa, ","tha-ap122:1.2":"aloko vipulo ahu; ","tha-ap122:1.3":"Pathavi ca pakampittha, ","tha-ap122:1.4":"sasagara sapabbata. ","tha-ap122:2.1":"Nemitta ca viyakamsu, ","tha-ap122:2.2":"buddho loke bhavissati; ","tha-ap122:2.3":"Aggo ca sabbasattanam, ","tha-ap122:2.4":"janatam uddharissati. ","tha-ap122:3.1":"Nemittanam sunitvana, ","tha-ap122:3.2":"jatipujamakasaham; ","tha-ap122:3.3":"Edisa pujana natthi, ","tha-ap122:3.4":"yadisa jatipujana. ","tha-ap122:4.1":"Sankharitvana kusalam, ","tha-ap122:4.2":"sakam cittam pasadayim; ","tha-ap122:4.3":"Jatipujam karitvana, ","tha-ap122:4.4":"tattha kalankato aham. ","tha-ap122:5.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","tha-ap122:5.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap122:5.3":"Sabbe satte abhibhomi, ","tha-ap122:5.4":"jatipujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap122:6.1":"Dhatiyo mam upatthanti, ","tha-ap122:6.2":"mama cittavasanuga; ","tha-ap122:6.3":"Na ta sakkonti kopetum, ","tha-ap122:6.4":"jatipujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap122:7.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap122:7.2":"yam pujamakarim tada; ","tha-ap122:7.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap122:7.4":"jatipujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap122:8.1":"Suparicariya nama, ","tha-ap122:8.2":"catuttimsa janadhipa; ","tha-ap122:8.3":"Ito tatiyakappamhi, ","tha-ap122:8.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap122:9.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap122:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap122:9.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap122:10.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma jatipujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap122:11.1":"Jatipujakattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap122:12.1":"Mahaparivaravaggo dvadasamo. ","tha-ap122:13.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap122:14.1":"Parivarasumangala, ","tha-ap122:14.2":"saranasanapupphiya; ","tha-ap122:14.3":"Citapuji buddhasanni, ","tha-ap122:14.4":"maggupatthanajatina; ","tha-ap122:14.5":"Gathayo navuti vutta, ","tha-ap122:14.6":"ganitayo vibhavihi. "}